convertToFlex

public java.util.Set<java.lang.Long> convertToFlex(java.util.List<java.lang.Long> systemIds,
                                                   java.lang.Long channelFamilyId,

Converts a a given list of servers to Flex. The conversion is stopped if "not_enough_slots" message shows up from the stored procedure. The return value shows how many systems successfully converted to flex

Parameters:

Returns:
